Arrest Record

Pablo Araya

Charges: Resisting arrest, damage to property

Statements:

Foreman's Statement: Mr. Araya was ordered to leave after indicating he wanted to reenter the mine, endangering himself and the safety of others. After being warned multiple times, he ran into the mine with a pickaxe and began damaging property.

Suspects Statement: Let me go. I need to save my brother.

